api.service.friendmanagement.Controller

Class FriendsRestController

  • java.lang.Object
    • api.service.friendmanagement.Controller.FriendsRestController

  • @Controller
public class FriendsRestController
extends java.lang.Object
    A Spring @Controller controller handling requests to view and modify User and friends information.

    Note that all the friends application classes are imported from the

  • Service layer: FriendsManagementService interface and its implementations
  • No repository layer is being used in the controller - the FriendsManagementService does everything
